<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.5.10">
<l>nellil kuvaḷai kaṇkāṭṭa nīril kumutam vāykāṭṭa</l>
<l>vallik kamalam mukaṅkāṭṭuṅ kaḻaṉi yaḻuntūr niṉṟāṉai</l>
<l>vallip potumpil kuyilkūvum maṅkai vēntaṉ parakālaṉ</l>
<l>collil polinta tamiḻmālai collap pāvam nillāvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If you say this renown Tamil garland in the words of Parakālaṉ,</l>
<l>King of Maṅkai where coocoos call in thickets with creepers,</l>
<l>About the one who stands in Aḻuntūr with fields</l>
<l rend="indent">where lily[-like] lotuses look like faces,</l>
<l>While red lilies in the water look like lips,</l>
<l>[and] while in the paddy fields dark lilies look like eyes,</l>
<l rend="indent">misfortune cannot last.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
